The Front Counter Greetings Sir or Miss, Come in, and Introduce yourself here at the front Counter. RIng the Bell for service, and place your order. Be aware that occassional hot peppers are served without warning.

The News Stand Discuss the current political or Economic situation or just things in the news! This is the place to get your Tabloid, Magazine , or multimedia news. Please provide refereneces and or Links for your 'quote and figures' posted from other webs in this forum.

The gift shop Entertainment and Media. The fun stuff! Movies, TV, Books, Concerts, anything that you think is fun! This is Brain Candy and it won't rot your teeth. So have a slice of life and cup of vitality to wash it down with.
The Cork Board Hey, it's a Diner, right??? So we gotta have a cork Board for menus and recipes!! Cooking, cleaning and buying, and other food recipe-related stuff

The Game/Reading Room This is for the gamers, the players, and the readers, the thrill seekers maybe even a spelling bee if you like. Play it, Read it, but make sure we all know the rules. Books or essasy of the month from the Customers always welcome.
